OL,5, Patients are being offered powerful    
OL,6, drugs and told they have attention     
OL,7, deficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD)  
OL,8, after unreliable online assessments, a 
OL,9, BBC investigation has discovered.      
OL,11,FThree private clinics diagnosed an     
OL,12,Fundercover reporter via video calls.   
OL,14,FBut a more detailed, in-person NHS     
OL,15,Fassessment showed he didn't have the   
OL,16,Fcondition.                             
